{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0ffe1e4063","title":"复程潜、陈明仁等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"663d4b255c","index":0,"year":1949,"month":8,"day":16,"articleId":"0ffe1e4063"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"e7b2bd7021","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"0ffe1e4063","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"1949年8月5日原国民党长沙绥靖公署主任程潜，副主任唐星、李默庵，国民党第一兵团司令官陈明仁，副司令官傅正模、刘进等发表起义通电。这是毛泽东和朱德给他们的复电。"}],"contents":[{"id":"5105aa9800","type":"title","text":"复程潜、陈明仁等电”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"0ffe1e4063"},{"id":"e7b2bd7021","type":"paragraph","text":"程潜将军、陈明仁将军暨全体起义将士们","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"0ffe1e4063"},{"id":"22d5b84e50","type":"paragraph","text":"接读八月五日通电，义正词严，极为佩感，中国人民解放事业的胜利，已成全世界公认的定局。美国帝国主义及其走狗蒋介石、李宗仁、白崇禧、图锡山等残余汇党不甘失败，尚图最后挣扎，必被迅速扫灭，已无疑义。诸公率三湘健儿，脱离反动阵营，参加人民革命，义声昭著，全国欢迎，南望湘云，谨致祝贺。尚望团结部属，与人民解放军亲密合作，并准备改编为人民解放军，以革命精神教育部队，改变作风，力求进步，为消灭残，解放全国人民而奋斗。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"0ffe1e4063"},{"id":"b68f080c20","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"0ffe1e4063"},{"id":"3a0cfaf613","type":"paragraph","text":"朱德","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"0ffe1e4063"},{"id":"6a1037134c","type":"paragraph","text":"一九四九年八月十六日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"0ffe1e4063"}],"page":{"id":"3ea6bc66bb","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"0ffe1e4063","start":142,"end":142}}}},"__N_SSG":true}